get.description:
Connect to the WebSocket server using Socket.IO client with JWT token for authentication.

## WebSocket Usage
This endpoint is accessed via WebSockets using Socket.IO.

```javascript
// Client-side code example
socket.emit('connect-to-websocket-server', payload, (response) => {
  if (response.event === 'error') {
    console.error('Error:', response.data);
  } else {
    console.log('Success:', response.data);
  }
});
```

> ⚠️ Note: This documentation is for WebSockets. Do not attempt to call this endpoint using HTTP.

